fields.title: Shaqa la'aanta dhalinyarada Soomaaliyeed
fields.description: Dhibaatada shaqo la'aanta ay keentay ee heysta dhalinyarada.
fields.content:

fields.title: Munaasabada Kudhawaaqida Ololaha Doorashada
fields.description: Waa dhacdo aad muhiim u ah oo shacabka Soomaaliyeed lagula socodsiin doono...
fields.content:
Shacabka Soomaaliyeed oo mudo dheer aad u dhowrayay arinta ku dhawaaqista ololoaha doorashada iyo in Mudane Jabril uu ka qeyb qaadan doono doorashada ayaa loo qabtay waqti.
Arintan ayaa ka farxisay dad farabadan oo taageero weyn u haya Mudane Jabril aaminsanna in uu dalka wax weyn uu ka bedeli karo.
Mudane Jabril oo ah nin khibrad aad u dheer u leh siyaasada geeska afrika iyo arimaha Soomaaliya gaar ahaan ayaa dadweynaha Soomaaliyeed hortooda ka muujin doono waxa uu ka damacsan yahay doorashada iyo dib udhiska iyo horumarinta dalka.

fields.title: Kusaabsan Hal Qaran
fields.description: Hal Qaran waa dhaqdhaqaaqa ujeedadiisu tahay badbaadinta Ummadda.
fields.content:

fields.title: About Hal Qaran
fields.description: Hal Qaran is a movement for justice and development for Somalia.
fields.content:
Hal Qaran was established by Somali Youth to overcome the luck of qualified leadership in the country. "The days of silence is over" says the Hal Qaran Movement.
